Maintainer: David Bescond <bescond@ilo.org>
Description: Provides functions to access and manipulate data from the
    ILOSTAT database <https://ilostat.ilo.org>, the International Labour
    Organization's repository of labour statistics. Supports bulk download
    of datasets, metadata retrieval, and tools for filtering, reshaping,
    and analysing data.
